  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIN CARDS</strong> is a horror-themed card game where you must build the ultimate deck to survive the nightmares of the Netherworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/e4a2a3be51981efd4aa74284688592b3.avif?t=1766930054\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Combine strategy and luck as you collect and purchase powerful cards, craft deadly combos, and face off against terrifying monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/603c46e5682abaea78b926526264e696.avif?t=1766930054\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Demons gradually grow stronger and more aggressive under the control of Delilah, the sinister voice of the Netherworld, a manipulative and mocking presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/9b977a6487a69944b3f1387e27a9d572.avif?t=1766930054\" width=170 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Each level introduces increasing difficulty and new mechanics like crafting, mining, and fishing. Craft hero items using resources and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/e092262e33fdcd62ac663b998ff1b3bc.avif?t=1766930054\" width=230 height=388 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Persistent Skilltree, Sin Coin Slots, Roulette-Style Games and Lore Expansions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/80155527c32bafeccd3f6209b2a99284.avif?t=1766930054\" width=120 height=182 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/73febadf058ce2e38e870b58221b7227.avif?t=1766930054\" width=236 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/f7304c451718abcec2d04b758f4edf3e.avif?t=1766930054\" width=312 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Each new level reveals more lore about the Sin Cards and the demons that inhabit the world. Some say the choices you make reveal the lengths you're willing to go to <span class=\"bb_strike\">survive</span> permadeath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/18bad826d0e7278c90f43c9288f359ad.webp?t=1766930054\" width=45 height=77 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIN CARDS</strong> is a horror-themed card game where you must build the ultimate deck to survive the nightmares of the Netherworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/e4a2a3be51981efd4aa74284688592b3.avif?t=1766930054\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Combine strategy and luck as you collect and purchase powerful cards, craft deadly combos, and face off against terrifying monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/603c46e5682abaea78b926526264e696.avif?t=1766930054\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Demons gradually grow stronger and more aggressive under the control of Delilah, the sinister voice of the Netherworld, a manipulative and mocking presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/9b977a6487a69944b3f1387e27a9d572.avif?t=1766930054\" width=170 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Each level introduces increasing difficulty and new mechanics like crafting, mining, and fishing. Craft hero items using resources and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/e092262e33fdcd62ac663b998ff1b3bc.avif?t=1766930054\" width=230 height=388 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Persistent Skilltree, Sin Coin Slots, Roulette-Style Games and Lore Expansions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/80155527c32bafeccd3f6209b2a99284.avif?t=1766930054\" width=120 height=182 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/73febadf058ce2e38e870b58221b7227.avif?t=1766930054\" width=236 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/f7304c451718abcec2d04b758f4edf3e.avif?t=1766930054\" width=312 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Each new level reveals more lore about the Sin Cards and the demons that inhabit the world. Some say the choices you make reveal the lengths you're willing to go to <span class=\"bb_strike\">survive</span> permadeath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411930/extras/18bad826d0e7278c90f43c9288f359ad.webp?t=1766930054\" width=45 height=77 /></span></p>",
